{"type": "article", "id": 24246, "title": "金马奖礼品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153118dyU41ZM0WObnYHlT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">茶籽堂（Cha Tzu Tang）是台湾一家以茶籽为基础发展洗护香油等产品的品牌。这是它们为第 51 届金马奖设计的礼品包装。包装上是版画家沐冉(Muran)采用木刻油印的方式画出的胭脂马，以点明金马奖，也拥有漂亮的手工感。盒子里用 5 个不一样的瓶子装有洗护用品，很精致。至少能让人感受到作为官方礼品的细心之处。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153114DcwHE8nU2I9TthZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.69907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153116C51HwGXanvYsc47e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153117YhtAc4xbins5BjSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}